    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>踏上一段轻松、治愈、风味十足的烹饪之旅，直至宇宙诞生原初之地。</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/59c57bf5695e34b69bf362ec81037484.poster.avif?t=1763423625\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/59c57bf5695e34b69bf362ec81037484.webm?t=1763423625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/59c57bf5695e34b69bf362ec81037484.mp4?t=1763423625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沉浸于五彩斑斓的彼岸世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《天堂之味》是一款佐有烹饪要素的RPG。你需要为超自然的妖怪神祗烹煮匠心独具的珍馐，或是给饥肠辘辘的灵魂准备果腹之物。在这个过程中，或许你还能靠一手好菜或许TA们的芳心……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在神界的烹饪之旅</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验独特的食谱系统——运用手头的各种食材与工具，满足一波波饥饿又挑剔的顾客。每个饥饿的灵魂都有自己的口味偏好，你的手腕能否满足他们的味蕾？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/b47eeff419f4035d19938b1b3d022d93.avif?t=1763423625\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras_big/b47eeff419f4035d19938b1b3d022d93.avif?t=1763423625 width=800 height=476 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与神灵相伴</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《天堂之味》，你将邂逅古怪的人神，奇妙的生物，以及前世恩怨尚未了解的灵魂。如果你以好菜好酒抚慰这些孤寂的生灵，他们或许会向你敞开心扉……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/b0cf3ab0062f73be4d029669732fc58b.avif?t=1763423625\" width=600 height=236 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每次轮回都将是独特的旅程</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一把游戏都不会重复，就像每一道料理的味道都不会重样：roguelite的系统让你可以收集奇妙的物品与能力，解锁奇遇事件，发现NPC背后隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/efa2d12f5b81fd18b45db0c2b5083030.avif?t=1763423625\" width=630 height=388 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在虚空建立温馨小窝</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四处搜罗资源，在巨鱼的腹中建造属于你的小旅馆。沿途会有各色旅人到访，他们可能成为你的帮手，或是带来各式奇谈怪论。让你的小天地，也成为他们放松身心的宁静绿洲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras/7b89d313107dd218a03663b97f8ff0f0.avif?t=1763423625\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835080/extras_big/7b89d313107dd218a03663b97f8ff0f0.avif?t=1763423625 width=800 height=304 /></span></p>",
